區，迷信可能來源於福建古代各大宗教基地眾多，以上種種導致了潮州式奸商文化<br />\n<br />\n香港黑社會潮州幫(新義安)<br />\n<br />\n瘋砸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:08:31.000Z","msg":"你小心喎咁講野，頭盔都唔帶"},{"pid":"7d296eafc43737e4e574a0a2994ed96250fbc0b6","tid":931173,"uid":56636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23b199336467648543f206e80952fa85e22a73c5","tid":931173,"uid":127469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:58:32.000Z","msg":"其實有冇IT人可以出嚟講吓呢種出錯有幾常見？ <br />\n照計應該要錯好多個steps先會出事？<br />\n有冇人識做錯嘅IT友？<br />\n 凶宅可唔可以民事索償條友\b或者外判嘅公司？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:08:48.000Z","msg":"洗鬼咩<br />\n<br />\n後台比sales自己入數啦<br />\n<br />\n就係驚呢啲情況比人賴"},{"pid":"01cea5c3621307f997c8d9f6f83283debdaf90d1","tid":931173,"uid":80103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:10:18.000Z","msg":"一個字<br />\n告佢老味！"},{"pid":"e3265322cf0f707853603429a2061be605af5dda","tid":931173,"uid":127469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d296eafc43737e4e574a0a2994ed96250fbc0b6","tid":931173,"uid":56636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23b199336467648543f206e80952fa85e22a73c5","tid":931173,"uid":127469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:58:32.000Z","msg":"其實有冇IT人可以出嚟講吓呢種出錯有幾常見？ <br />\n照計應該要錯好多個steps先會出事？<br />\n有冇人識做錯嘅IT友？<br />\n 凶宅可唔可以民事索償條友\b或者外判嘅公司？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:08:48.000Z","msg":"洗鬼咩<br />\n<br />\n後台比sales自己入數啦<br />\n<br />\n就係驚呢啲情況比人賴"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"Sorry可唔可以簡單解釋一下咩叫 後台比sales自己入數？"},{"pid":"70905dc7548f14cca9cbfcd14efb0356717999e4","tid":931173,"uid":125423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"187cbe2503e9a44396a9a1b087dfda3b9150e0da","tid":931173,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c882bc60ac3069abdc737f23eb8cb38b69c68cca","tid":931173,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53c7be3c4a287bf6867500eabd3bcc57111